  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n`PanacheQuery` expose `Hibernate` session filters but there isn't supports for `@EntityGraph`s.\r\nEvaluate to expose `@EntityGraph` in `PanacheQuery`.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nA trivial implementation may add some methods to `PanacheQuery` as `#fetchGraph(String graphName)`/`#loadGraph(String graphName)` or `#graph(String graphType, String graphName)`.\r\nIDK If more complex actions are required during deployment (for example recording `@NamedEntityGraph`s to be setted in `io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.common.runtime.PanacheHibernateRecorder`)",
